title: Openscapes JupyterHub Access
text:
Openscapes JupyterHub Access 

Openscapes runs JupyterHubs for organizations that are starting to explore cloud computing. These hubs provide a place for people to host workshops and experiment with cloud-based workflows.
The hubs are set up and administered by our amazing partners at 2i2c.
Access the login page for your organization below:
